videos.headline: Hill dodges defender, scores 18-yard TD
videos.description: TCU QB Kenny Hill showcases his agility, dodging a Kansas defender and scampering into the end zone for an 18-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: 67-yard run puts Kansas near goal line
videos.description: Kansas QB Ryan Willis completes a short pass to LaQuvionte Gonzalez, who runs 67-yards to TCU's 2-yard line and picks up the first down.

videos.headline: Kenny Hill 3rd interception of the day
videos.description: Kenny Hill pass intercepted Greg Allen return for 20 yds to the TCU 25

videos.headline: Kansas rushes for a 21-yard TD
videos.description: Kansas QB Ryan Willis decides not to pass and takes it to the house himself for a 21-yard rushing touchdown in the third quarter against TCU.

videos.headline: TCU captializes on the live ball for a big gain
videos.description: Kenny Hill looses the ball but the play is not over and he picks it up and runs for a nice gain.

videos.headline: TCU takes late lead on 34-yard field goal
videos.description: Brandon Hatfield hits a field goal from 34 yards out to give TCU a 24-23 lead over Kansas late in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Kansas misses game-winning FG
videos.description: Jayhawks kicker Matthew Wyman attempts to connect on a 54-yard, game-winning field goal but misses, ending the game in a one-point loss against TCU.
